item.dc:creator: @n10si_t n10si t
item.description:
@n10si_t wrote:

[quote=“I Vain I”][quote author=n10si t link=topic=493604.msg3609067#msg3609067 date=1306377612]
oh god.

Back around age 10 and 11, me and a few friends found a private server called range-x. Anyone remember that server? Jesus Christ. We would play this server for hours and hours and hours on end. We would have sleepovers and just play that for like 36 hours at a time. I remember one time we had a 3 day weekend in February and we played, non-stop, for 65 FUCKING HOURS. No sleep. it was AWESOME. one of us literally fell out of the chair and collapsed on the floor. me and the other guy took his bandos. he cried after he woke up.

YEEEAAAAHHHH
[/quote]guys have sleepovers…?[/quote]

well what else do you want to call hanging out and sleeping over?

slumber partay
